"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">30</A>
Consuls in 132 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN> when the inquiry into the acts of Tiberius Gracchus were made.


