They were consuls together, 282 and 278 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN> and censors, 275 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN>


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note33" HREF="
